{"tid":2274991,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–體外細胞培植的醫療用途(1)","createTime":"2020-11-06T23:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T06:19:08.000Z","uid":38861,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"71950c4408038b529f0dca46810c082b2700de6f","tid":2274991,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T23:11:03.000Z","msg":"1975年，James Rheinwald 及Howard Green兩名科學家成功設立方法，只需拿取一小部份的人體皮膚組織，再加上老鼠細胞的幫助下，便能夠在體外無止境地培養出屬於該名人士的皮膚細胞(Ref1)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gfuKWEp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgfuKWEp.jpg&h=38a5b614&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖2)80年代，分別有兩名5-6歲的男孩遭受到全身97-98%的燒傷。<br />\n醫生利用科學家的研究，拿取僅餘的皮膚組織，在實驗室體外培植並製造出皮膚組織，嘗試移植到各燒傷位置上(Ref2)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EmF2Jjs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmF2Jjs.png&h=69b47597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖3)兩名男孩分別經過21及24星期的治療後，身體表面的98%及85%均得以康復痊癒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1XoDgEv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1XoDgEv.png&h=bc25a55a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中接近50%的康復位置，均是依靠實驗室體外培植的皮膚組織移植而成。<br />\n<br />\n兩位科學家的貢獻，亦因而開拓了利用體外培植細胞作醫療及檢測藥物效果的道路。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣了解更多相關話題的話，請多多正評。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=b3d2090a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=f7d64873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=159d065d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0092867475800018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0092867475800018&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=5a289ed2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0092867475800018</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0140673681900064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0140673681900064&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9uzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=37c0d003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S0140673681900064</a>"},{"pid":"a9fb3cdc4d22e97d7e3f3d7a4574b7e5b9b7a3eb","tid":2274991,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T23:16:25.000Z","msg":"支持但係對呢個topic冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/m